The evidence with the title 'Deficits falling (from way up) - factcheck.org ' says Aug 1, 2013  ... In recent speeches , president Obama has repeatedly claimed that “ our deficits are falling at the fastest rate in 60 years . ”The White House says he's referring to the decline in the deficit as apercentage of the nation 's economy from 2009 to 2012 . But that's not the “ fastest rate ” of deficit reduction in 60 years. 
